                            [<![CDATA[
                                Your team is scheduled to be competing at the SCVA Red Rock Rave #2 in April 2021 and I wanted to provide a reminder that hotels will be going live for reservations on Tuesday (Groups) 7am PST or Friday at 7am PST (Individual reservations) via the housing agency for the tournament, KC Sportshousing.

