                                RED ROCK RAVE #2
                                What - SCVA Qualifier - Red Rock Rave #2
                                When - April 16, 17, 18
                                Hotel Dates - Check in would be on April 15 and check out on April 18
                                Where - Tournament Location - Mandalay Bay Convention Center, Las Vegas

                                Families are responsible for their own hotel bookings.
                            ]]>
