                        <note>
                            <![CDATA[
                                1) Follow the hotel booking link. Enter the Access Code and hit “Make a Reservation” (See link and access code below)
                                   Please be advised that emails ending in .NET are blocking the hotel system’s emails. We highly recommend using a .COM email address or taking a picture of your confirmation.
                                2) Follow through the prompts until you get to where you enter your personal information. When asked for Club/Team Code, please enter the code JUST AS IT IS LISTED BELOW or your reservation may be cancelled and/or will not count towards the Support the Sport – Stay and Play Policy.
                                3) Please complete all necessary information and ensure you receive a confirmation email directly from the hotel.
                                    a. The credit card provided will be charged a one-night deposit (plus taxes) for each individual room booked. If the card holder responsible for all charges covered by this agreement will not be present at check-in, you must fill out the hotel’s credit card authorization form PRIOR to your arrival date. Please contact KC Sports Housing if you are in need of this form.
                                    b. The name provided for check-in will be the ONLY individual allowed to check-in at the hotel. Please ensure they are over 21 and someone is over 21 in every room.

                                    Tournament: Red Rock Rave – JNQ #2
                                    Hotel: Delano
                                    Booking Link: https://book.passkey.com/e/50154163
                                    Access Code: RRRDL0421
